com.joliciel.talismane.lexicon

Class CompactLexicalEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.lexicon.CompactLexicalEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LexicalEntry, WritableLexicalEntry, java.io.Serializable

    public class CompactLexicalEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements WritableLexicalEntry, java.io.Serializable
    A compact lexical entry, using a related CompactLexicalEntrySupport to efficiently store reference data.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli

      java.lang.String getAttribute(java.lang.String attribute)
      Get any attribute for this lexical entry, as a String.
      If the attribute is a LexicalAttribute, it will return the corresponding attribute.
      If it is a String, will try to match it to an existing OtherAttribute, and return the corresponding value.
      If the attribute is a List, the items will be joined together into a single pipe-delimited String.
